 data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span data-contrast=\"auto\">USD 259 is preparing students to be successful in college and more, with having SRG for students a while back that did not use our SRG weren\u2019t prepared for the grading system in college and other educational fields according to<\/span><span data-contrast=\"auto\"> Assistant Principal Charlie Bartsch, <\/span><\/p>\n<p><span data-contrast=\"auto\">\u201cIn college they don\u2019t use SRG which would make USD 259 goals no where they are wanting them too. While now at Northwest we can prepare students for their next level of education and help them achieve their goals,\u201d<\/span><span data-contrast=\"auto\"> Bartsch said. <\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Students at Northwest were happy with this change, CJ Mertes (12) was one of the students that were happy with this change. <\/span><\/p>\n<p><span data-contrast=\"auto\">\u201cI was happy with this change because it felt like it would bring my grade down and cause me to have stress about what my grades were,\u201d Mertes said.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>&nbsp;The SRG grading system is a grading scale that has been increasingly used in classes. It is a system used by our teachers to help kids on their behalf with their understanding of the subject or even unit.&nbsp; But here at Northwest High School the grading system is reverting back to how it normally was&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":128,"featured_media":8699,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"ngg_post_thumbnail":0,"footnotes":""},"categories":[4,12],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.northwestexplorer.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/86